---
title: Double Saucy Pesto Beef Meatballs with Spinach & Rocket Couscous
description: These beef meatballs have a flavourful twist, can you guess what it is? It’s our favourite cheesy, nutty and herby condiment, mixed right in with the mince - pesto! This vibrant addition packs a punch with flavour. Serve these meatballs atop a fluffy couscous, coated in a rich tomato sauce for your new favourite meatball combo!
